sentences: Kenneth Duncan Jr. (born May 15, 1993), better known as BRS Kash is an American rapper from Atlanta, Georgia.
Kenneth Duncan Jr. grew up in Atlanta listening to hip hop artists like Kilo Ali, Raheem the Dream, and Outkast.
On November 22, 2019, BRS Kash released his first single "Throat Baby (Go Baby)".
In August 2020, it was announced he signed with Love Renaissance and Interscope Records.
On January 22, 2021, BRS Kash released his debut mixtape Kash Only, including the remix of "Throat Baby (Go Baby)" featuring DaBaby and City Girls.
